item.title: CVE-2021-36909|2024-09-16T20:21:59.621Z -- webfactory%20ltd. -- wp%20reset%20pro
item.description: Authenticated Database Reset vulnerability in WordPress WP Reset PRO Premium plugin (versions <= 5.98) allows any authenticated user to wipe the entire database regardless of their authorization. It leads to a complete website reset and takeover.
